---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '@components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '@components/Footer.astro';

const title = "Terms of Service | Zero Method";
const description = "The rules of using Zero Method";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <Header />

  <main class="pt-32 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-navy-300">
        <p class="text-sm text-navy-400 mb-8">Last updated: April 2, 2026</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">1. The Basics</h2>
        <p>By using Zero Method, you agree to these terms. If you don't agree, don't use the site.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">2. What You're Buying</h2>
        <p>You're purchasing:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>25 AI prompts (PDF + Markdown)</li>
          <li>10 email templates</li>
          <li>1 year of free updates</li>
          <li>Personal use license</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">3. What You Can Do</h2>
        <p>You can:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Use the prompts for your own work</li>
          <li>Share with your immediate team (up to 5 people)</li>
          <li>Modify prompts for your specific needs</li>
          <li>Print for personal reference</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">4. What You Can't Do</h2>
        <p>You cannot:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Resell the prompts or templates</li>
          <li>Distribute publicly (on websites, social media, etc.)</li>
          <li>Create derivative products for sale</li>
          <li>Claim the content as your own</li>
          <li>Share with more than 5 team members (buy the Agency license for that)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">5. Refunds</h2>
        <p>30-day money-back guarantee. Not satisfied? Email <a href="mailto:support@thezeromethod.com" class="text-gold-500 hover:text-gold-400">support@thezeromethod.com</a> for a full refund. No questions asked.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">6. Updates</h2>
        <p>You get free updates for 1 year from purchase date. After that, you keep the version you have, but new updates require a new purchase.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">7. No Guarantees</h2>
        <p>We test our prompts, but results vary. We don't guarantee:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Specific time savings (depends on your workflow)</li>
          <li>AI output quality (depends on the AI model)</li>
          <li>Business results</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Use at your own discretion.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>Our liability is limited to the purchase price ($19). We're not responsible for indirect damages, lost profits, etc.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">9. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>We may update these terms. Major changes will be emailed to customers.</p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">10. Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions? <a href="mailto:support@thezeromethod.com" class="text-gold-500 hover:text-gold-400">support@thezeromethod.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
